63
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:19,310
See you.

64
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:21,750
Take care.

65
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:22,310
See you.

66
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:24,190
- Hang in there.
- Yeah.

67
00:03:25,510 --> 00:03:27,070
We have to upgrade our equipment.

68
00:03:27,070 --> 00:03:28,380
The more time we spend on it,

69
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,030
the more we may get...

70
00:03:30,070 --> 00:03:31,580
Hey. I realized something lately.

71
00:03:32,380 --> 00:03:33,470
Why aren't you guys

72
