83
00:04:06,350 --> 00:04:07,910
Get him some hot water.

84
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:10,860
You're so dumb.

85
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:19,260
Stop it!

86
00:04:27,110 --> 00:04:27,780
You.

87
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:28,820
Tell me.

88
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:30,110
How many people do we have here?

89
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:35,020
14...

90
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:36,550
There are 14 of us.

91
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:39,700
