do basic Math, huh? My boss.

92
00:04:39,770 --> 00:04:40,900
How many hands do we have?

93
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:43,430
28.

94
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:44,780
28, right?

95
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:46,310
We have 28 hands here.

96
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:48,580
But no one here
can pour him some water?

97
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,780
