99
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:56,820
Show me your handicap ID.

100
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:01,670
But you guys are interns.

101
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:04,310
Does that mean
we have to serve you like a servant?

102
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:06,020
Take out the contract.

103
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:08,700
