105
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:14,220
Buddy, I came here to learn something.

106
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,670
Use your brain and think.

107
00:05:15,670 --> 00:05:18,380
I studied for 22 years.

108
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,380
Do you think I'm here
to serve you, a man

109
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:21,220
