117
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:37,700
Don't pick it up.

118
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,580
Bring it here.

119
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,900
The interns are excluded again.

120
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:48,460
You only order seven cups
of coffee every time.

121
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:51,140
You were too stingy
to order Starbucks.

122
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:53,700
A few cups of Nestle espresso
should be fine, right?

123
00:05:54,900 --> 00:05:56,430
Aren't interns living humans?

124
00:05:57,550 --> 00:05:58,780
I'll order them for you now.

125
00:05:59,220 --> 00:06:00,070
No need for that!

126
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:02,020
All of you

127
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:04,990
