133
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:21,190
I...

134
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:22,670
I...

135
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:24,820
Spineless.

136
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:26,220
You won't achieve anything.

137
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:39,780
You didn't take your snacks.

138
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:51,550
Give me your hand.

139
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:52,310
