Why is no one refilling it?

142
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:13,870
I'll do it.

143
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,340
No need for that.

144
00:07:15,380 --> 00:07:16,780
You go ahead. I'll do it myself.

145
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:17,220
I'll do it.

146
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:18,310
I can do it myself.

147
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:19,870
- That's right.
- Okay.

148
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:20,460
You go ahead.

149
00:07:25,670 --> 00:07:27,750
Dai Daji, come here immediately!

150
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:42,460
Get ready to be an official employee.

151
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:49,040
Tell the HR Department
to do your paperwork

152
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,900
