153
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:52,670
Thank you, Director Wen.

154
00:07:56,220 --> 00:07:57,430
Leave the water on my desk.

155
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:03,630
I'll leave it here.

156
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:12,020
