162
00:08:22,510 --> 00:08:23,310
Jingshu.

163
00:08:23,550 --> 00:08:24,240
Dongting.

164
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,060
It's your first time
asking me out for a meal.

165
00:08:29,020 --> 00:08:30,020
Do you need anything?

166
00:08:31,220 --> 00:08:33,220
