167
00:08:33,910 --> 00:08:35,460
I want to treat you to a meal as well.

168
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:37,190
You don't need to pay me back.

169
00:08:37,190 --> 00:08:38,550
Pay your school fees with it.

170
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:40,820
Nope.

171
00:08:41,460 --> 00:08:42,670
You're Jingjing's boyfriend.

172
00:08:42,740 --> 00:08:44,670
