173
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:45,700
Jingshu.

174
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:48,340
Don't you understand my intention?

175
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:55,730
I'll stop beating around the bush.

176
00:08:58,910 --> 00:08:59,820
I like you.

177
00:09:00,220 --> 00:09:01,500
I want to be together with you.

178
00:09:04,970 --> 00:09:06,100
