180
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:09,220
I'll deal with Jingjing somehow.

181
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:11,190
I truly fancy you.

182
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:13,700
And, this sum was supposed
to be your school fees anyway.

183
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:15,910
Our family has
an apartment near Xuezhiqiao.

184
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,390
- You don't need to...
- Li Dongting!

185
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:20,220
I didn't believe them
when they exposed you.

186
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:22,030
How could you mess around with her?

187
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,500
What are you talking about?

188
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,910
What am I talking about?

189
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:26,070
What are you talking about?

190
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:26,620
I...

191
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:29,070
I didn't say anything.

192
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,100
Just lent her some money.

193
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:31,270
Stop lying to me!

194
00:09:31,390 --> 00:09:33,220
I heard everything you guys said!

195
00:09:33,220 --> 00:09:34,620
Jingjing, you're mistaken.

196
00:09:34,620 --> 00:09:36,150
Can you have some empathy for once?

197
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:38,860
Jingshu is born into a poor family.
She's having a rough time.

198
00:09:39,190 --> 00:09:40,670
What's wrong with lending her money?

199
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:44,270
Are you sure you're helping her?

200
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:46,270
You're just trying to court her!

201
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:47,860
Forget it. You should stop.

202
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,190
Let go of me!

203
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:51,340
You ingrate!

204
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:53,190
I paid for your dorm!

205
00:09:53,220 --> 00:09:54,950
I gave you everything you wore!

206
00:09:54,950 --> 00:09:55,910
