209
00:10:00,620 --> 00:10:03,220
Li Dongting, have you lost your mind?

210
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:06,910
Why must it be her?

211
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:10,860
You're unreasonable!

212
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,100
