217
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:32,430
Stop pretending.

218
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:35,580
I'll show everyone your true colors.

219
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:43,910
Here she is.

220
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:45,130
- Jingjing.
- She's here.

221
00:10:45,130 --> 00:10:46,010
She's here.

222
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:49,820
Come! Everyone, let's do a kind deed!

223
00:10:49,950 --> 00:10:52,950
Shen Jingshu, a student
majoring in Accounting,

224
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:55,550
is unable to pay her school fees
due to her poor background.

225
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:57,700
Please donate to her if you can.

226
00:10:57,700 --> 00:10:59,310
- Hurry!
- Come!

227
00:10:59,310 --> 00:11:00,310
Donate to her!

228
00:11:00,310 --> 00:11:01,820
Come on, everyone!

229
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:02,550
Why are you going?

230
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:04,310
- Don't leave.
- Don't leave.

231
00:11:04,430 --> 00:11:05,860
I think Jingshu is shy.

232
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:07,820
- She doesn't want girls' money.
- Don't leave.

233
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:08,340
Don't go.

234
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:10,910
- Guys, do a kind deed.
- Where are you going?

235
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:13,980
If so, why aren't you taking our money?

236
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:16,670
Do you think money
is the only thing she wants?

237
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:19,390
What she desires is love.

238
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,270
Do you have to do this?

239
00:11:22,740 --> 00:11:25,270
What? You think
you still have any dignity left?

240
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:30,070
Don't leave.

241
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:36,150
Just leave. Hurry.

242
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:37,740
Shen Jingshu, open the door!

243
00:11:37,860 --> 00:11:39,390
Let me see which room you're living in.

244
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,310
Hurry!

245
00:11:40,310 --> 00:11:41,430
Let's start the party!

246
00:11:41,430 --> 00:11:42,040
Jingshu?

247
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:42,390
Let's see

248
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,590
